{"tid":1751142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"0013 祖堯要記者 有冇人可以call 因為唔俾分開點票","createTime":"2019-11-24T16:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T16:32:27.000Z","uid":97716,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"438880a6ae711f16ffa73a367d1cf9340417811a","tid":1751142,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"ec6256b39a100ab4b335190eb5e83bfc3d9f368d","tid":1751142,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b00f941f99d16b27e5fde0b75e2a526f56d38063","tid":1751142,"uid":90883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d457e8935b30c28259c41b6548365e1a7d26fc67","tid":1751142,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"點解要分，有外來票箱？"},{"pid":"6291b3422a7faee7180f2bcf4c510a865ce6c165","tid":1751142,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f650963bd954e64a118a66f43712c955a76436e","tid":1751142,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535b0273ad9cb155f6c8353b30021a0735ca32b3","tid":1751142,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"45e9ce9495cd9ed1e68688a01aa4629f67f6e85e","tid":1751142,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"0347582773f11ac33004b4915cbfbae7a720e16e","tid":1751142,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:14:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e916276f0f406734bb61b2b5e5cd39345f12f3db","tid":1751142,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:14:49.000Z","msg":"可以分開數票箱既票數架<br />\n<br />\n在場企硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4de62f2abc73ae090877df886031f35b74236a","tid":1751142,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:15:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6467ed04f4511797f0f83b47652645d8527c8faa","tid":1751142,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bb7f0bd4a91f8190842574efb2211ff4a23fc6d","tid":1751142,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e916276f0f406734bb61b2b5e5cd39345f12f3db","tid":1751142,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:14:49.000Z","msg":"可以分開數票箱既票數架<br />\n<br />\n在場企硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:17:17.000Z","msg":"法例寫要一齊點<br />\n第541F章 《選舉管理委員會(選舉程序)(區議會)規例》 第76條 點票<br />\n<br />\n(1)在每個點票站的點票區，該點票站的選票必須由有關投票站主任按本條規定處理。 (2003年第125號法律公告)<br />\n(2)大點票站的投票站主任必須在該大點票站點票時，將被指定為該大點票站的投票站最少一個投票箱內的選票，與以下的選票混和 &mdash;&mdash; (2009年第131號法律公告；2012年第11號第57條)<br />\n(a)自一個或多於一個小投票站或特別投票站送遞至該大點票站的選票；及<br />\n(b)自一個或多於一個選票分流站或一個或多於一個專用投票站(視何者屬適當而定)送遞至該大點票站的選票。 (2009年第197號法律公告)"},{"pid":"9542a997cab5133b62329d298534cd5f3209720d","tid":1751142,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad01e4d4ce84a140aa8f25fe1af15d14ddd57b3d","tid":1751142,"uid":120807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61a43ce5968072a922f72f2d2a260f79839361d2","tid":1751142,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bb7f0bd4a91f8190842574efb2211ff4a23fc6d","tid":1751142,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e916276f0f406734bb61b2b5e5cd39345f12f3db","tid":1751142,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:14:49.000Z","msg":"可以分開數票箱既票數架<br />\n<br />\n在場企硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:17:17.000Z","msg":"法例寫要一齊點<br />\n第541F章 《選舉管理委員會(選舉程序)(區議會)規例》 第76條 點票<br />\n<br />\n(1)在每個點票站的點票區，該點票站的選票必須由有關投票站主任按本條規定處理。 (2003年第125號法律公告)<br />\n(2)大點票站的投票站主任必須在該大點票站點票時，將被指定為該大點票站的投票站最少一個投票箱內的選票，與以下的選票混和 &mdash;&mdash; (2009年第131號法律公告；2012年第11號第57條)<br />\n(a)自一個或多於一個小投票站或特別投票站送遞至該大點票站的選票；及<br />\n(b)自一個或多於一個選票分流站或一個或多於一個專用投票站(視何者屬適當而定)送遞至該大點票站的選票。 (2009年第197號法律公告)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有巴打咁講<br />\n<br />\n17. 為確保投票保密，少於 500 名登記選民的小投票站的選票及所有專用投票站的選票（已在選票分流站按地方選區分類）會被送往所屬的大點票站，與其他選民在該票站投下的選票混合後，才予以點算。<br />\n<br />\n份嘢有啲舊但係應該一直都係咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr09-10/chinese/panels/ca/papers/ca0419cb2-1289-3-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr09-10%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fca%2Fpapers%2Fca0419cb2-1289-3-c.pdf&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJb6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=eeffd0b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr09-10/chinese/panels/ca/papers/ca0419cb2-1289-3-c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"c65890a2a069ae20973a59901fc9827d9545c548","tid":1751142,"uid":30721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:30:34.000Z","msg":"祖堯要記者，推"},{"pid":"3e92970dec0f83920e1fce6c88fe617dcd1e186c","tid":1751142,"uid":30721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"祖堯要記者，推"},{"pid":"f86af651dc74580ebddaea1a4ee06593ae042800","tid":1751142,"uid":297806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:32:02.000Z","msg":"仲點緊？"},{"pid":"684cd7c071e339c7c977541afafeb80110cc6b7d","tid":1751142,"uid":8086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}